Privacy Policy for Screen Chopper
Last updated: 03/21/2025

Screen Chopper does not collect, store, or share any personal data.
The extension operates entirely within the user's browser, processing screenshots locally without transmitting any data to external servers.

What information do we collect?
None. The extension does not store, share, or analyze user data.

How is your information used?
Your data stays on your device. Screenshots are processed locally and saved as PNG files in a zip archive.

Third-Party Services

Screen Chopper does not integrate with or share data with third parties.

Changes to this Policy

This policy may be updated if new features require changes. Any modifications will be reflected here.

If you have questions, contact chubes@chubes.net.
